name: 14K Rose Gold Filled 18 Gauge Hoops, Hammered Texture
description:

name: 14K Rose Gold Filled Sleeper Hoop Earrings

You have a choice of either 20 gauge or 18 gauge for the hoops.

Rose Gold has a lovely coppery look, also known as pink gold.

They have a total length of 16mm, and have an inner diameter of 13mm.

To put in, with a gentle twist motion, pull gently in opposite directions, so hoop will keep its shape, as shown in the last photo.

description:

This bracelet can be dressed up or down, and will take you from day to night. Sure to become a wardrobe staple.

Brass has the look of gold, but with a fraction of the price. Brass is an alloy of Copper and Zinc. 

The cuff is aprroximately 1/4 inch in width and has an inner diametre of 2.5ins., and the opening is 1.25ins. The bracelet can be adjusted slightly, but will keep its shape, as it is work hardened.

Brass will develop a lovely darker patina over time, and can be polished with a jewellery cloth or mild abrasive.
